<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home - Bitbox</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background: url('path-to-your-background-image.jpg') no-repeat center center/cover;
        }

        header {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            left: 20px;
        }

        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .content {
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            max-width: 800px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 4em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        button {
            background-color: #ff6900;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 18px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #e05d00;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <img src="../statics/BitBox_logo1.png" alt="Bitbox Logo" width="100">
    </header>
    <div class="hero">
        <h1>Welcome to Bitbox Support</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>At Bitbox, we specialize in creating innovative solutions that empower our customers. Our cutting-edge technology and dedicated team work together to bring you the best products and services in the industry.</p>
        <p>Our mission is to provide top-notch customer service and ensure that our clients have the tools they need to succeed. Whether you're looking for the latest in device management or comprehensive warranty support, Bitbox has got you covered.</p>
        <p>Discover more about our offerings and how we can help you achieve your goals.</p>
        <a href="http://localhost:5001/check-device"><button>Check Your Device Info</button></a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
